{"tid":1285780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有咩好見面談判？","createTime":"2019-07-04T16:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T20:27:29.000Z","uid":4705,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"75d51c168cb22843c572fd4df3cd9bed9133628d","tid":1285780,"uid":4705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:37:32.000Z","msg":"係咪得我一個覺得其實冇嘢好傾？<br />\n<br />\n訴求全部好清晰，冇需要見面談判，冇要斟酌嘅地方<br />\n有咩好傾？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一： 全面撤回《引渡條例》<br />\n二： 成立獨立調查委員會調查事件<br />\n三： 釋放被捕人士並承諾不檢控任何示威者<br />\n四： 撤銷暴動定性<br />\n五： 立即在八三一框架外重新啟動政改<br />\n六： 實行雙普選，納入公民提名及政黨提名於行政長官提名程序、廢除功能組別</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n一係就應承一係就繼續扮聽唔到我哋爭取<br />\n無論係公開定閉門談判都好，作用係咩？<br />\n喺記者面前都可以做錄音機<br />\n談判有啲咩意義？<br />\n<br />\n幾年前談判過，都有Live架，結果呢？"},{"pid":"9aed9f16ee4102f9dcb3efaae7b77cdcd00fd425","tid":1285780,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/hJy832m.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhJy832m.gif&h=43898d62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我光頭佬有興趣屌林奠<br />\n點聯絡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5815d73e6469c5df98c170931a2d465fd03f4e1","tid":1285780,"uid":4705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9aed9f16ee4102f9dcb3efaae7b77cdcd00fd425","tid":1285780,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/hJy832m.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhJy832m.gif&h=43898d62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我光頭佬有興趣屌林奠<br />\n點聯絡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/